data.description: Welcome to 6300 Silverbell Ct.  This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath bi level home has been well loved and maintained.  This home has new vinyl siding and roof in 2019.  The outside features a new expanded deck the overlooks the nice sized corner lot.  Home has been freshly painted.  All appliances stay.  Easy convenient access to I-70, U.S. 35 and close to grocery, shopping and restaurants. Schedule your showing today!  1610 Square Ft
